    \ Everyday throughout the world, there are companies trying to create something great.  What they are lacking is the Talent within a specific discipline to get their project completed. \

    \ \

    \ With the global shift to so many of people working from home rather than commuting to an office, we can be more effective, businesses can be more cost-efficient and we can have a cleaner planet.\

    \
    \
    \

    \ \ TalentEarth is leading the way when it comes to building virtual teams to tackle projects worldwide and we have several patents to prove it. \ \

    \ \

    \ \ Whether you're looking for one-to-one work or looking to combine your Talent with a team that is taking on something great - we only have two words for you.\ \
    \ \ \ \ JOIN US.\ \ \ \

    2025 Update on The Creative Economy

    \
    \
    \     \
    \
    \
    \
    The 2025 Otis College Report on the Creative Economy highlights California\'92s continued leadership in art, design, entertainment, and new media. Despite challenges from recent strikes and economic shifts, the report reveals a resilient creative sector that employs over 760,000 people and drives nearly one in ten jobs statewide\'97affirming California\'92s role as a global hub for creative innovation.
